704090f-a.title: Brooklyn: Elton Street - Wortman Avenue
704090f-a.text:
Elton Street, south from Wortman Ave., showing a city street, which
continues as a winding farm road, on its way towards Jamaica Bay.
July 5, 1934.
P L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
704090f-a.folder: Elton Street & Wortman Avenue, Brooklyn, NY

707451f-a.title: Brooklyn: Wortman Ave. - Elton St.
707451f-a.text:
457-473 Wortman Ave., north side, from Elton to Linwood Streets, showing
Soiefer Milk and Cream Farm. Also seen is row of homes on Elton Street, east
side, north from Wortman Ave.
July 5, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
